---
const title = 'Panel central Mizo';
---

<!doctype html>
<html lang="es">
	<head>
		<meta charset="UTF-8" />
		<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
		<meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
		<link rel="icon" type="image/png" href="/favicon.png" />
		<title>{title}</title>
		<script is:inline>
			window.tailwind = window.tailwind || {};
			window.tailwind.config = {
				theme: {
					extend: {
						colors: {
							'accent-main': '#1877f2',
							'accent-soft': '#e7f0ff',
							'accent-hover': '#166fe5',
						},
					},
				},
			};
		</script>
		<script is:inline src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
		<style>
			.view-panel { display: none; }
			.view-panel.active { display: block; }
			.nav-active { background: #1877f2; color: white; box-shadow: 0 10px 25px rgb(24 119 242 / 0.18); }
		</style>
	</head>
	<body class="min-h-screen bg-slate-100 text-slate-950">
		<main class="mx-auto flex min-h-screen w-full max-w-[1600px] flex-col lg:flex-row">
			<aside class="border-b border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 lg:sticky lg:top-0 lg:h-screen lg:w-72 lg:border-b-0 lg:border-r">
				<a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
					<img src="/mizo-logo.png" alt="Mizo" class="h-10 w-auto" onerror="this.src='/mizo-logo.svg';" />
					<div>
						<p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-accent-main">Mizo Admin</p>
						<h1 class="text-xl font-black">Panel central</h1>
					</div>
				</a>

				<nav id="admin-nav" class="mt-6 grid grid-cols-2 gap-2 lg:grid-cols-1">
					<button class="admin-nav-btn nav-active rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-black" data-view="catalogo">Catálogo Maestro</button>
					<button class="admin-nav-btn rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-black text-slate-600 hover:bg-accent-soft" data-view="vitrina">
						<span class="block">Publicar en web</span>
						<span class="mt-0.5 block text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide opacity-70">/equipamiento</span>
					</button>
					<button class="admin-nav-btn rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-black text-slate-600 hover:bg-accent-soft" data-view="proyectos">
						<span class="block">Proyectos web</span>
						<span class="mt-0.5 block text-[0.65rem] font-semibold uppercase tracking-wide opacity-70">/ #proyectos</span>
					</button>
					<button class="admin-nav-btn rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-black text-slate-600 hover:bg-accent-soft" data-view="cotizador">Cotizador</button>
					<button class="admin-nav-btn rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-black text-slate-600 hover:bg-accent-soft" data-view="auditoria">Auditoría</button>
					<button class="admin-nav-btn rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-black text-slate-600 hover:bg-accent-soft" data-view="pedidos">Pedidos</button>
					<button class="admin-nav-btn rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-left text-sm font-black text-slate-600 hover:bg-accent-soft" data-view="leads">Formularios web</button>
				</nav>

				<div class="mt-6 rounded-2xl border border-orange-200 bg-orange-50 p-4 text-sm text-orange-950">
					<p class="font-black">¿Qué productos ve el público?</p>
					<p class="mt-1">Entra a <button type="button" class="font-black text-accent-main underline admin-goto-vitrina">Publicar en web</button> para elegir qué equipos aparecen en <a href="/equipamiento" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="font-black underline">/equipamiento</a>.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="mt-3 rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 bg-accent-soft p-4 text-sm text-slate-700">
					<p class="font-black text-slate-950">Fuente única</p>
					<p class="mt-1">Este panel lee el catálogo cifrado central de Mizo y evita catálogos paralelos en PHP.</p>
				</div>
			</aside>

			<section class="flex-1 p-4 sm:p-6 lg:p-8">
				<div id="login-card" class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-md rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-7 shadow-sm">
					<p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-main">Acceso privado</p>
					<h2 class="mt-2 text-2xl font-black">Administrador Central Mizo</h2>
					<p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-500">Un solo acceso para catálogo, vitrina, cotizaciones, leads y pedidos. La clave debe coincidir con <code>ADMIN_PASSWORD</code> del servidor.</p>
					<form id="login-form" class="mt-6 space-y-3">
						<input id="password" type="password" autocomplete="current-password" placeholder="Clave privada" class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 text-sm outline-none focus:border-accent-main focus:ring-2 focus:ring-blue-100" required />
						<button class="w-full rounded-2xl bg-accent-main px-4 py-3 text-sm font-black text-white hover:bg-accent-hover">Entrar</button>
						<p id="login-error" class="hidden text-sm font-semibold text-red-600">No se pudo abrir el panel. Revisa la clave o el archivo datos-privados.json.</p>
					</form>
				</div>

				<div id="panel" class="hidden">
					<header class="mb-6 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between">
						<div>
							<p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-main">Administración unificada</p>
							<h2 id="view-title" class="mt-1 text-3xl font-black">Catálogo Maestro</h2>
							<p id="catalog-meta" class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500"></p>
						</div>
						<button id="logout" class="self-start rounded-full border border-slate-300 bg-white px-4 py-2 text-sm font-black text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50">Cerrar sesión</button>
					</header>

					<section id="view-catalogo" class="view-panel active">
						<div id="catalog-summary" class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4"></div>
						<div class="mt-5 rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
							<div class="flex flex-col gap-3 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
								<div>
									<h3 class="text-xl font-black">Catálogo unificado</h3>
									<p class="text-sm text-slate-500">Productos disponibles para publicación, costos y cotizaciones.</p>
								</div>
								<input id="catalog-search" type="search" placeholder="Buscar por SKU, marca, producto o proveedor..." class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 text-sm lg:max-w-md" />
							</div>
							<p id="catalog-count" class="mt-4 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500"></p>
							<div id="catalog-list" class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 xl:grid-cols-2"></div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<section id="view-vitrina" class="view-panel">
						<div class="rounded-3xl border border-orange-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
							<div class="rounded-2xl border border-orange-100 bg-orange-50/80 p-4">
								<p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-orange-700">Paso a paso</p>
								<ol class="mt-2 list-decimal space-y-1 pl-5 text-sm leading-6 text-orange-950">
									<li>Elige si quieres publicar <strong>todo el catálogo</strong> o solo <strong>productos seleccionados</strong>.</li>
									<li>En modo selección, marca los productos con la casilla ☑ y pulsa <strong>Guardar selección</strong>.</li>
									<li>Revisa el resultado en <a href="/equipamiento" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-black text-accent-main underline">/equipamiento</a>.</li>
								</ol>
							</div>

							<div class="mt-5 grid gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
								<button type="button" id="showcase-mode-all" class="showcase-mode-card rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 text-left transition hover:border-orange-300">
									<p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-400">Modo 1</p>
									<p class="mt-1 text-lg font-black text-slate-950">Catálogo completo</p>
									<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Todos los productos del catálogo aparecen en la web pública.</p>
								</button>
								<button type="button" id="showcase-mode-curated" class="showcase-mode-card rounded-2xl border-2 border-slate-200 bg-white p-4 text-left transition hover:border-orange-300">
									<p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-wide text-slate-400">Modo 2</p>
									<p class="mt-1 text-lg font-black text-slate-950">Selección manual</p>
									<p class="mt-1 text-sm text-slate-600">Tú eliges qué productos mostrar marcando las casillas.</p>
								</button>
							</div>

							<div id="showcase-mode-banner" class="mt-4 hidden rounded-2xl px-4 py-3 text-sm font-semibold"></div>

							<div class="mt-5 flex flex-col gap-3 lg:flex-row lg:items-center lg:justify-between">
								<div>
									<h3 class="text-xl font-black">Qué publicar en /equipamiento</h3>
									<p id="showcase-status" class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">Cargando configuración de la vitrina...</p>
								</div>
								<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
									<button id="publish-all-showcase" type="button" class="rounded-full border border-orange-300 bg-orange-50 px-5 py-2.5 text-xs font-black text-orange-800 hover:bg-orange-100">Aplicar catálogo completo</button>
									<button id="save-showcase" type="button" class="rounded-full bg-accent-main px-5 py-2.5 text-xs font-black text-white hover:bg-accent-hover">Guardar selección</button>
									<a href="/equipamiento" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="rounded-full border border-slate-300 px-5 py-2.5 text-xs font-black text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50">Ver en sitio</a>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div id="showcase-curated-tools" class="mt-4 hidden flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
								<input id="showcase-search" type="search" placeholder="Buscar producto para activar en la web..." class="w-full rounded-2xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 text-sm lg:max-w-md" />
								<div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
									<button id="showcase-select-all" type="button" class="rounded-full border border-slate-300 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-black text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50">Marcar todos</button>
									<button id="showcase-select-none" type="button" class="rounded-full border border-slate-300 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-black text-slate-700 hover:bg-slate-50">Desmarcar todos</button>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div id="showcase-list" class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 xl:grid-cols-2"></div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<section id="view-proyectos" class="view-panel">
						<div class="rounded-3xl border border-slate-200 bg-white p-5 shadow-sm">
							<div class="rounded-2xl border border-blue-100 bg-accent-soft/60 p-4">
								<p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-main">Portada del sitio</p>
								<p class="mt-2 text-sm leading-6 text-slate-700">
									Administra la sección <strong>Algunos trabajos que hemos desarrollado</strong> en la página de inicio.
									Puedes subir varias fotos por proyecto. Los cambios se publican al guardar.
								</p>
								<p class="mt-2 text-sm">
									<a href="/#proyectos" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="font-black text-accent-main underline">Ver en la web</a>
								</p>
							</div>

							<div class="mt-5 flex flex-col gap-3 sm:flex-row sm:items-center sm:justify-between">
								<div>
									<h3 class="text-xl font-black">Proyectos publicados</h3>
									<p id="proyectos-status" class="mt-1 text-sm font-semibold text-slate-500">Cargando proyectos...</p>
								</div>
								<button id="proyecto-new" type="button" class="rounded-full bg-brand-orange px-5 py-2.5 text-xs font-black text-white hover:bg-brand-orange-hover">+ Nuevo proyecto</button>
							</div>

							<div id="proyectos-list" class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 xl:grid-cols-2"></div>

							<div id="proyecto-editor" class="mt-6 hidden rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 bg-slate-50 p-5">
								<div class="flex items-start justify-between gap-3">
									<div>
										<p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-brand-orange">Editor de proyecto</p>
										<h4 id="proyecto-editor-title" class="mt-1 text-lg font-black text-slate-950">Nuevo proyecto</h4>
									</div>
									<button id="proyecto-editor-close" type="button" class="rounded-full border border-slate-300 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-black text-slate-700 hover:bg-white">Cerrar</button>
								</div>

								<input id="proyecto-id" type="hidden" />
								<div class="mt-4 grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
									<label class="block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
										Nombre del proyecto
										<input id="proyecto-title" type="text" class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 text-sm" placeholder="Ej. Auditorio municipal de Frutillar" />
									</label>
									<label class="block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
										Tipo / rubro
										<input id="proyecto-type" type="text" class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 text-sm" placeholder="Ej. Educación, Iglesia, Auditorio" />
									</label>
								</div>

								<label class="mt-4 block text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
									Descripción del trabajo
									<textarea id="proyecto-description" rows="4" class="mt-1 w-full rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-4 py-3 text-sm" placeholder="Qué se instaló, alcance, equipos principales..."></textarea>
								</label>

								<div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-4">
									<label class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
										<input id="proyecto-published" type="checkbox" class="h-4 w-4 rounded border-slate-300" checked />
										Publicado en la web
									</label>
									<label class="text-sm font-bold text-slate-700">
										Orden
										<input id="proyecto-sort" type="number" min="1" class="ml-2 w-20 rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" value="1" />
									</label>
								</div>

								<div class="mt-5">
									<p class="text-sm font-black text-slate-800">Imágenes del proyecto</p>
									<p class="mt-1 text-xs text-slate-500">Puedes subir varias fotos. Se mostrarán en un carrusel en la portada.</p>
									<div id="proyecto-images" class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-2 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-3 lg:grid-cols-4"></div>
									<div class="mt-4 flex flex-wrap items-center gap-3">
										<input id="proyecto-image-input" type="file" accept="image/jpeg,image/png,image/webp" multiple class="block w-full max-w-md text-sm text-slate-600 file:mr-3 file:rounded-full file:border-0 file:bg-accent-main file:px-4 file:py-2 file:text-xs file:font-black file:text-white hover:file:bg-accent-hover" />
										<p id="proyecto-upload-status" class="text-xs font-semibold text-slate-500"></p>
									</div>
								</div>

								<div class="mt-6 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
									<button id="proyecto-save" type="button" class="rounded-full bg-accent-main px-6 py-3 text-sm font-black text-white hover:bg-accent-hover">Guardar proyecto</button>
									<button id="proyecto-delete" type="button" class="hidden rounded-full border border-red-300 bg-red-50 px-6 py-3 text-sm font-black text-red-700 hover:bg-red-100">Eliminar proyecto</button>
								</div>
							</div>
						</div>
					</section>

					<section id="view-cotizador" class="view-panel">
						<div class="overflow-hidden rounded-3xl border border-blue-200 bg-white shadow-sm">
							<div class="border-b border-blue-100 bg-blue-50 px-5 py-4">
								<p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-accent-main">Cotizador profesional</p>
								<div class="mt-1 flex flex-col gap-2 sm:flex-row sm:items-end sm:justify-between">
									<div>
										<h3 class="text-2xl font-black">Nueva cotización Mizo</h3>
										<p class="text-sm font-semibold text-blue-900">Correlativo seguro, productos del catálogo, ítems manuales, PDF y envío por email.</p>
									</div>
									<span id="quote-next-number" class="inline-flex self-start rounded-full bg-white px-4 py-2 text-xs font-black text-accent-main shadow-sm">Presupuesto: M1001</span>
								</div>
							</div>

							<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-5 p-5 xl:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1fr)_380px]">
								<div class="space-y-5">
									<div class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-4 md:grid-cols-2">
										<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-4">
											<div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
												<p class="text-sm font-black">Datos fijos de Mizo</p>
												<button id="save-quote-config" type="button" class="text-xs font-black text-accent-main">Guardar config</button>
											</div>
											<div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
												<input id="quote-company-name" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Razón social" />
												<input id="quote-company-tax-id" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="RUT" />
												<input id="quote-company-phone" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Teléfono" />
												<input id="quote-company-email" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="ventas@mizo.cl" />
												<input id="quote-company-address" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Dirección" />
												<input id="quote-company-website" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Sitio web" />
												<input id="quote-company-logo" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="URL/Base64 logo" />
											</div>
										</div>

										<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-4">
											<p class="text-sm font-black">Datos del cliente</p>
											<div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 sm:grid-cols-2">
												<input id="quote-client-name" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Nombre cliente" />
												<input id="quote-client-email" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Email" />
												<input id="quote-client-phone" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Teléfono" />
												<input id="quote-client-rut" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="RUT / Código" />
												<input id="quote-client-address" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm sm:col-span-2" placeholder="Dirección / comuna" />
											</div>
										</div>
									</div>

									<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-4">
										<p class="text-sm font-black">Agregar ítems</p>
										<div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 lg:grid-cols-[minmax(0,1.2fr)_90px_130px_auto]">
											<select id="quote-catalog-product" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm">
												<option value="">Importar producto del catálogo Mizo</option>
											</select>
											<input id="quote-catalog-qty" type="number" min="1" value="1" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Cant." />
											<input id="quote-catalog-price" inputmode="numeric" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Precio opcional" />
											<button id="add-catalog-quote-item" type="button" class="rounded-xl bg-slate-950 px-4 py-2 text-xs font-black text-white">Agregar catálogo</button>
										</div>
										<div class="mt-3 grid grid-cols-1 gap-3 lg:grid-cols-[1fr_120px_90px_130px_auto]">
											<input id="quote-manual-name" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Ítem manual / servicio externo" />
											<input id="quote-manual-sku" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="SKU temporal" />
											<input id="quote-manual-qty" type="number" min="1" value="1" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Cant." />
											<input id="quote-manual-price" inputmode="numeric" class="rounded-xl border border-slate-300 px-3 py-2 text-sm" placeholder="Precio unit." />
											<button id="add-manual-quote-item" type="button" class="rounded-xl bg-accent-main px-4 py-2 text-xs font-black text-white">Agregar manual</button>
										</div>
									</div>

									<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-4">
										<div class="flex items-center justify-between gap-3">
											<p class="text-sm font-black">Detalle de cotización</p>
											<button id="clear-quote-items" type="button" class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-500 hover:text-red-600">Limpiar ítems</button>
										</div>
										<div id="quote-items-list" class="mt-3 space-y-2"></div>
									</div>
								</div>

								<aside class="space-y-4">
									<div class="rounded-2xl bg-slate-950 p-5 text-white">
										<p class="text-xs font-black uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-blue-200">Total presupuesto</p>
										<p id="quote-total" class="mt-2 text-3xl font-black">$0</p>
										<p id="quote-saved-link" class="mt-3 text-xs font-semibold text-white/70"></p>
									</div>
									<div class="rounded-2xl border border-slate-200 p-4">
										<p class="text-sm font-black">Condiciones comerciales</p>
